'''Mthatha''' (kgale ke ''Umtata'', toropo kgolo kgolo ya Transkei) ke toropo kgolo kgolo gofeta [[King Sabata Dalindyebo Mmusogae]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša O.R. Tambo]] wa diporofense [[Kapa Bohlabela]] (Eastern Cape) ka moka [[Afrika Borwa]]. 

Toropo e na le airport, K. D. Matanzima Airport, lebitso ke ya Transkei leader Kaiser Matanzima. Highway tša N2 e tsamaiya mô [[Durban]], [[East London]] le [[Cape Town]], e suka Mthatha.

